ne-shot: the `BubbleMenuNodeSelector` function + `BubbleMenuNodeSelectorProps` in `node-selector.tsx`\n- LinkSelector: `packages/editor/src/ui/bubble-menu/link-selector.tsx`\n- Compound namespace: `packages/editor/src/ui/bubble-menu/index.ts`\n- Existing tests for reference: `root.spec.tsx`, `group.spec.tsx`, `item.spec.tsx`\n\n### Out of scope\n\n- Custom item rendering (use Layer 0 for that)\n- Theme/styling (that's Layer 2, PRODUCT-1509)\n- Documentation (that's PRODUCT-1505, blocked by this ticket)\n- Excluding individual node types from the NodeSelector dropdown (use Layer 0 `NodeSelector.Root omit` prop)\n",
