            "content": "# Button Bubble Menu Primitives — Implementation Plan\n\n> **For Claude:** REQUIRED SUB-SKILL: Use superpowers:executing-plans to implement this plan task-by-task.\n\n**Goal:** Extract button bubble menu from dashboard into `@react-email/editor` as compound component primitives, then migrate dashboard to consume them.\n\n**Architecture:** Follows the existing `link-bubble-menu/` compound component pattern — Root (wraps tiptap BubbleMenu + context), Toolbar (conditional visibility), EditLink (action button). Minimal set: just enough to migrate the dashboard.\n\n**Tech Stack:** React, TipTap v3, Vitest + happy-dom, Biome, tsdown\n\n**Linear:** PRODUCT-1508 (OSS primitives), PRODUCT-1514 (dashboard migration)\n\n---\n\n## Setup\n\n### Task 0: Worktree setup (react-email repo)\n\n**Step 1: Add .worktrees to .gitignore**\n\nIn `/Users/jopcmelo/Developer/resend/react-email/.gitignore`, add at the end:\n\n```\n.worktrees\n```\n\n**Step 2: Commit**\n\n```bash\ngit add .gitignore\ngit commit -m \"chore: add .worktrees to gitignore\"\n```\n\n**Step 3: Create worktree**\n\n```bash\ngit worktree add .worktrees/button-bubble-menu -b feat/editor-button-bubble-menu-primitives\n```\n\n**Step 4: Install deps and verify baseline**\n\n```bash\ncd .worktrees/button-bubble-menu/packages/editor\npnpm install\npnpm test\n```\n\nExpected: all tests pass (208 currently)\n\n---\n\n## OSS Primitives (react-email repo)\n\nAll work in `.worktrees/button-bubble-menu/packages/editor/src/ui/button-bubble-menu/`.\n\nReference: `link-bubble-menu/` directory for patterns.\n\n### Task 1: Context\n\n**Files:**\n- Create: `src/ui/button-bubble-menu/context.tsx`\n- Test: `src/ui/button-bubble-menu/context.spec.tsx`\n\n**Step 1: Write the test**\n\n```tsx\n// context.spec.tsx\nimport { renderHook } from '@testing-library/react';\nimport { useButtonBubbleMenuContext } from './context';\n\ndescribe('useButtonBubbleMenuContext', () => {\n  it('throws when used outside a Provider', () 