            "content": "# PRODUCT-1509 + PRODUCT-1510: Default Theme CSS\n\n> **For Claude:** REQUIRED SUB-SKILL: Use superpowers:executing-plans to implement this plan task-by-task.\n\n**Goal:** Ship an optional default theme CSS file that styles all 4 bubble menus with CSS custom properties for consumer theming. Fix missing CSS exports.\n\n**Architecture:** Single `default.css` file authored with `@import` for Layer 0 layout CSS, flattened at build time via `postcss` + `postcss-import` (Radix Themes pattern). CSS custom properties with light defaults + dark mode via `prefers-color-scheme` and `.dark` class.\n\n**Tech Stack:** CSS, PostCSS, postcss-import\n\n**Repo:** `react-email` (`/Users/jopcmelo/Developer/resend/react-email`)\n**Branch:** `feat/editor-default-theme-css` off `feat/ai-oss-editor`\n**Linear:** PRODUCT-1509, PRODUCT-1510\n\n---\n\n### Task 1: Create branch\n\n**Step 1:** Create branch from `feat/ai-oss-editor`\n\n```bash\ncd /Users/jopcmelo/Developer/resend/react-email\ngit checkout feat/ai-oss-editor && git pull origin feat/ai-oss-editor\ngit checkout -b feat/editor-default-theme-css\n```\n\n---\n\n### Task 2: Fix missing CSS exports in package.json\n\n**Files:**\n- Modify: `packages/editor/package.json`\n\n**Step 1:** Add missing exports for button and image bubble menu CSS\n\nAdd to `exports` field:\n\n```json\n\"./styles/button-bubble-menu.css\": \"./dist/ui/button-bubble-menu/button-bubble-menu.css\",\n\"./styles/image-bubble-menu.css\": \"./dist/ui/image-bubble-menu/image-bubble-menu.css\"\n```\n\n**Step 2:** Verify build copies these files\n\n```bash\npnpm build --filter=@react-email/editor\nls dist/ui/button-bubble-menu/button-bubble-menu.css\nls dist/ui/image-bubble-menu/image-bubble-menu.css\n```\n\n**Step 3:** Commit\n\n```bash\ngit add packages/editor/package.json\ngit commit -m \"fix: add missing CSS exports for button and image bubble menus\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### Task 3: Add postcss + postcss-import as devDependencies\n\n**Files:**\n- Modify: `packages/editor/package.json`\n\n**Step 1:** Install postcss and postcss-import\n\n```bash\ncd packages/editor\npnpm add -D postcss postcss-import\n```\n\nNote: postcss@8.5.6 already exists in the monorepo (preview-server, apps/web), so this pins to a compatible version.\n\n**Step 2:** Commit\n\n```bash\ngit add packages/editor/package.json ../../pnpm-lock.yaml\ngit commit -m \"chore: add postcss and postcss-import for theme CSS build\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### Task 4: Update build script to process theme CSS with postcss\n\n**Files:**\n- Modify: `packages/editor/scripts/copy-css.mjs`\n- Modify: `packages/editor/package.json` (build script)\n\n**Step 1:** Update `copy-css.mjs` to process theme files through postcss-import\n\nThe script should:\n1. Copy non-theme CSS files as-is (existing behavior)\n2. For files in `ui/themes/`, run through postcss with postcss-import to flatten `@import` statements\n\n```js\nimport { cpSync, mkdirSync, readFileSync, readdirSync, statSync, writeFileSync } from 'node:fs';\nimport { dirname, join, relative } from 'node:path';\nimport postcss from 'postcss';\nimport postcssImport from 'postcss-import';\n\nconst src = 'src';\nconst dist = 'dist';\n\nconst themeProcessor = postcss([postcssImport()]);\n\nasync function processTheme(full, dest) {\n  const css = readFileSync(full, 'utf8');\n  const result = await themeProcessor.process(css, { from: full, to: dest });\n  mkdirSync(dirname(dest), { recursive: true });\n  writeFileSync(dest, result.css);\n  console.log(`processed ${relative(src, full)}`);\n}\n\nfunction walk(dir, themeFiles) {\n  for (const entry of readdirSync(dir)) {\n    const full = join(dir, entry);\n    if (statSync(full).isDirectory()) {\n      walk(full, themeFiles);\n    } else if (entry.endsWith('.css')) {\n      const rel = relative(src, full);\n      const dest = join(dist, rel);\n      if (rel.startsWith('ui/themes/')) {\n        themeFiles.push({ full, dest });\n      } else {\n        cpSync(full, dest, { recursive: true });\n        console.log(`copied ${rel}`);\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n\nconst themeFiles = [];\nwalk(src, themeFiles);\n\nfor (const { full, dest } of themeFiles) {\n  await processTheme(full, dest);\n}\n```\n\n**Step 2:** Commit\n\n```bash\ngit add packages/editor/scripts/copy-css.mjs\ngit commit -m \"feat: process theme CSS through postcss-import to flatten @imports\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### Task 5: Create `default.css` theme file\n\n**Files:**\n- Create: `packages/editor/src/ui/themes/default.css`\n\n**Step 1:** Create the theme file\n\n```css\n/* Default theme for @react-email/editor bubble menu primitives.\n *\n * Opt-in: import '@react-email/editor/themes/default.css';\n *\n * Override any variable on a parent element:\n *   .my-editor { --re-bg: #1a1a1a; --re-border: #333; }\n */\n\n/* Layer 0: layout (inlined at build time via postcss-import) */\n@import '../bubble-menu/bubble-menu.css';\n@import '../link-bubble-menu/link-bubble-menu.css';\n@import '../button-bubble-menu/button-bubble-menu.css';\n@import '../image-bubble-menu/image-bubble-menu.css';\n\n/* ----------------------------------------------------------------\n * CSS custom properties — light defaults\n * ---------------------------------------------------------------- */\n\n:root {\n  --re-bg: #fff;\n  --re-border: #e5e5e5;\n  --re-text: #1c1c1c;\n  --re-text-muted: #6b6b6b;\n  --re-hover: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);\n  --re-active: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);\n  --re-pressed: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);\n  --re-separator: #e5e5e5;\n  --re-radius: 0.75rem;\n  --re-radius-sm: 0.5rem;\n  --re-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 4px 6px -4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n  --re-danger: #dc2626;\n  --re-danger-hover: rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.1);\n}\n\n/* ----------------------------------------------------------------\n * Dark mode — prefers-color-scheme\n * ---------------------------------------------------------------- */\n\n@media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {\n  :root {\n    --re-bg: #1c1c1c;\n    --re-border: #2e2e2e;\n    --re-text: #ececec;\n    --re-text-muted: #a0a0a0;\n    --re-hover: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);\n    --re-active: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.09);\n    --re-pressed: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.09);\n    --re-separator: #2e2e2e;\n    --re-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3), 0 4px 6px -4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n    --re-danger: #f87171;\n    --re-danger-hover: rgba(248, 113, 113, 0.15);\n  }\n}\n\n/* ----------------------------------------------------------------\n * Dark mode — .dark class override\n * ---------------------------------------------------------------- */\n\n.dark {\n  --re-bg: #1c1c1c;\n  --re-border: #2e2e2e;\n  --re-text: #ececec;\n  --re-text-muted: #a0a0a0;\n  --re-hover: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);\n  --re-active: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.09);\n  --re-pressed: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.09);\n  --re-separator: #2e2e2e;\n  --re-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3), 0 4px 6px -4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n  --re-danger: #f87171;\n  --re-danger-hover: rgba(248, 113, 113, 0.15);\n}\n\n/* ----------------------------------------------------------------\n * Root containers\n * ---------------------------------------------------------------- */\n\n[data-re-bubble-menu],\n[data-re-link-bm],\n[data-re-btn-bm],\n[data-re-img-bm] {\n  background: var(--re-bg);\n  border: 1px solid var(--re-border);\n  border-radius: var(--re-radius);\n  box-shadow: var(--re-shadow);\n  overflow: hidden;\n}\n\n/* ----------------------------------------------------------------\n * Toolbars (link, button, image bubble menus)\n * ---------------------------------------------------------------- */\n\n[data-re-link-bm-toolbar],\n[data-re-btn-bm-toolbar],\n[data-re-img-bm-toolbar] {\n  gap: 0;\n}\n\n/* Dividers between toolbar items */\n[data-re-link-bm-toolbar] > * + *,\n[data-re-btn-bm-toolbar] > * + *,\n[data-re-img-bm-toolbar] > * + * {\n  border-left: 1px solid var(--re-border);\n}\n\n/* ----------------------------------------------------------------\n * Item groups (text bubble menu)\n * ---------------------------------------------------------------- */\n\n[data-re-bubble-menu-group] + [data-re-bubble-menu-group] {\n  border-left: 1px solid var(--re-border);\n}\n\n/* ----------------------------------------------------------------\n * Item buttons (all bubble menus)\n * ---------------------------------------------------------------- */\n\n[data-re-bubble-menu-item],\n[data-re-link-bm-item],\n[data-re-btn-bm-item],\n[data-re-img-bm-item] {\n  color: var(--re-text);\n  transition: background-color 0.15s;\n}\n\n[data-re-bubble-menu-item]:hover,\n[data-re-link-bm-item]:hover,\n[data-re-btn-bm-item]:hover,\n[data-re-img-bm-item]:hover {\n  background: var(--re-hover);\n}\n\n[data-re-bubble-menu-item]:active,\n[data-re-link-bm-item]:active,\n[data-re-btn-bm-item]:active,\n[data-re-img-bm-item]:active {\n  background: var(--re-active);\n}\n\n/* Active / pressed state */\n[data-re-bubble-menu-item][data-active],\n[data-re-bubble-menu-item][aria-pressed='true'] {\n  background: var(--re-pressed);\n  color: var(--re-text);\n}\n\n/* ----------------------------------------------------------------\n * Separator (text bubble menu)\n * ---------------------------------------------------------------- */\n\n[data-re-bubble-menu-separator] {\n  background: var(--re-separator);\n}\n\n/* ----------------------------------------------------------------\n * Node Selector\n * ---------------------------------------------------------------- */\n\n[data-re-node-selector-trigger] {\n  color: var(--re-text);\n  transition: background-color 0.15s;\n}\n\n[data-re-node-selector-trigger]:hover {\n  background: var(--re-hover);\n}\n\n[data-re-node-selector-trigger]:active {\n  background: var(--re-active);\n}\n\n[data-re-node-selector-content] {\n  background: var(--re-bg);\n  border: 1px solid var(--re-border);\n  border-radius: var(--re-radius);\n  box-shadow: var(--re-shadow);\n  padding: 0.25rem 0;\n  margin-top: 0.25rem;\n}\n\n[data-re-node-selector-item] {\n  color: var(--re-text-muted);\n  border-radius: var(--re-radius-sm);\n  transition: background-color 0.15s, color 0.15s;\n}\n\n[data-re-node-selector-item]:hover {\n  background: var(--re-hover);\n  color: var(--re-text);\n}\n\n[data-re-node-selector-item][data-active] {\n  color: var(--re-text);\n}\n\n/* ----------------------------------------------------------------\n * Link Selector (text bubble menu)\n * ---------------------------------------------------------------- */\n\n[data-re-link-selector-trigger] {\n  color: var(--re-text);\n  transition: background-color 0.15s;\n}\n\n[data-re-link-selector-trigger]:hover {\n  background: var(--re-hover);\n}\n\n[data-re-link-selector-trigger][aria-pressed='true'] {\n  background: var(--re-pressed);\n}\n\n[data-re-link-selector-form] {\n  background: var(--re-bg);\n  border: 1px solid var(--re-border);\n  border-radius: var(--re-radius);\n  box-shadow: var(--re-shadow);\n  padding: 0.25rem;\n}\n\n[data-re-link-selector-input] {\n  color: var(--re-text);\n}\n\n[data-re-link-selector-input]::placeholder {\n  color: var(--re-text-muted);\n}\n\n[data-re-link-selector-apply] {\n  color: var(--re-text);\n  border-radius: var(--re-radius-sm);\n  transition: background-color 0.15s;\n}\n\n[data-re-link-selector-apply]:hover {\n  background: var(--re-hover);\n}\n\n[data-re-link-selector-unlink] {\n  color: var(--re-danger);\n  border-radius: var(--re-radius-sm);\n  transition: background-color 0.15s;\n}\n\n[data-re-link-selector-unlink]:hover {\n  background: var(--re-danger-hover);\n}\n\n/* ----------------------------------------------------------------\n * Link Bubble Menu Form\n * ---------------------------------------------------------------- */\n\n[data-re-link-bm-form] {\n  background: var(--re-bg);\n  border: 1px solid var(--re-border);\n  border-radius: var(--re-radius);\n  box-shadow: var(--re-shadow);\n  padding: 0.25rem;\n}\n\n[data-re-link-bm-input] {\n  color: var(--re-text);\n}\n\n[data-re-link-bm-input]::placeholder {\n  color: var(--re-text-muted);\n}\n\n[data-re-link-bm-apply] {\n  color: var(--re-text);\n  border-radius: var(--re-radius-sm);\n  transition: background-color 0.15s;\n}\n\n[data-re-link-bm-apply]:hover {\n  background: var(--re-hover);\n}\n\n[data-re-link-bm-unlink] {\n  color: var(--re-danger);\n  border-radius: var(--re-radius-sm);\n  transition: background-color 0.15s;\n}\n\n[data-re-link-bm-unlink]:hover {\n  background: var(--re-danger-hover);\n}\n```\n\n**Step 2:** Commit\n\n```bash\ngit add packages/editor/src/ui/themes/default.css\ngit commit -m \"feat: add default theme CSS with custom properties for all bubble menus\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### Task 6: Add theme export to package.json\n\n**Files:**\n- Modify: `packages/editor/package.json`\n\n**Step 1:** Add theme export\n\n```json\n\"./themes/default.css\": \"./dist/ui/themes/default.css\"\n```\n\n**Step 2:** Commit\n\n```bash\ngit add packages/editor/package.json\ngit commit -m \"feat: export default theme CSS as @react-email/editor/themes/default.css\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### Task 7: Version bump\n\n**Files:**\n- Modify: `packages/editor/package.json`\n\n**Step 1:** Bump version to `0.0.0-experimental.13`\n\n**Step 2:** Commit\n\n```bash\ngit add packages/editor/package.json\ngit commit -m \"chore: bump to 0.0.0-experimental.13\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### Task 8: Build and verify\n\n**Step 1:** Build the package\n\n```bash\npnpm build --filter=@react-email/editor\n```\n\n**Step 2:** Verify all CSS files in dist\n\n```bash\nls -la dist/ui/themes/default.css\nls -la dist/ui/bubble-menu/bubble-menu.css\nls -la dist/ui/link-bubble-menu/link-bubble-menu.css\nls -la dist/ui/button-bubble-menu/button-bubble-menu.css\nls -la dist/ui/image-bubble-menu/image-bubble-menu.css\n```\n\n**Step 3:** Verify default.css has NO @import statements (they should be flattened)\n\n```bash\ngrep '@import' dist/ui/themes/default.css\n```\n\nExpected: no output (all @imports resolved and inlined).\n\n**Step 4:** Verify default.css contain